channel.title: It was working LAST night
channel.description:
This is very strange. I had the server working one night, shut it off over night, went to start it up the next day and I get this error. The only thing that's changed is the addition of new character files where my friends have been logging in. I've changed nothing else.
Please help! Thanks.
